explanation.summary: Kt qu in tm  cho thy c chn on Block nhnh tri. Tuy nhin, cc ch s o c v hnh nh in tim li khng hon ton ph hp vi chn on ny, cn c bc s chuyn khoa xem xt thm.
explanation.details: Chn on Block nhnh tri (LBBB) thng c ngha l tn hiu in n bung tim bn tri b chm tr, khin tim co bp khng ng b. iu ny thng lm cho sng QRS trn in tm  rng ra (thng trn 0.12 giy). Tuy nhin, hnh nh sng in tim cho thy cc sng QRS trng hp, v ch s thi gian QRS o c l 0.062 giy, nm trong gii hn bnh thng. Nhp tim ca bn l 96.89 ln/pht, nm trong ngng bnh thng (60-100 ln/pht). Ch s bin thin nhp tim (HRV RMSSD) l 13.99 ms, kh thp, c th gi  v s gim kh nng iu ha nhp tim ca c th.
explanation.recommendations: Bn cn mang kt qu ny i khm chuyn khoa tim mch cng sm cng tt  bc s nh gi li ton din v lm r chn on, cng nh xem xt cc ch s khc.
